Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the city of Toras.\NThe sun is setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll rest here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Silver? It's been a long time since you smelled the scent of women.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! Come on, Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're waiting for us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-yo, Silver!{tag line from the American TV serial, The Lone Ranger}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the legendary\N knight Takeru Yamato,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,an outstanding warrior for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born as a child of the gods,\N but fate has ordained
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that he must wander in the human realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He himself does not know his origins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But numerous heroic deeds are attributed to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and his name is known everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The people yearn for his coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,His appearance is like a ray of sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one who hasn't heard of Yamato Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:30.44,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(320,430)}Dragon Knight Gaiden
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That must be the famous cathedral of Toras.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's quite a lot of activity here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop that boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That scoundrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Return the property you stole,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We should just kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? You don't just hit children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get bent out of shape, stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to get back what this dirty little rascal stole from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to fight me is suicide, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you stole something, then you'd best cough it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,or I'll leave you with these {\i1}friendly{\i0} gentlemen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. I take it you're satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right now, stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. The priest has...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool. That's nobody else's business!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's split!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back my coin purse, immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You've probably just started in this line of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I really that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if even I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go on like this, you'll lose both your hands for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably hungry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I haven't eaten anything for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm inviting you to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to promise me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're with me, no thieving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's all, then your purse is safe from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean everyone's purses. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Jodi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, that one's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru, when are we finally going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, that can wait a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! But that one's sweet too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru, how long do I \Nhave to wait for food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see women!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since I've seen a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Leonardo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest, obey me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Toras still needs more women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Thy will be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon this city will be transformed into a swamp of lust, Great Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just us, Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's about time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring these women to Venezza the moneylender right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible. We counted the money twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron! Who's talking about money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This purse also contained an important drug that I {\i1}must{\i0} have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Important drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the little guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize that thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And because he probably knows about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be better if you disposed of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need a confederate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go at once and get to work. Every second counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You appear quite desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That voice... I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shade? As always, your appearance is very theatrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Leonardo likes me to keep an eye on his subordinates, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you understand that I have to find this drug soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At any cost, this city must not discover who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Leonardo has not yet been informed about this little mishap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you assist me in retrieving this drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. But I'm doing it my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm really in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have an amazing appetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough for the next two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Those portions were for three grown men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, is it true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that you lost sight of your sister when you entered the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't have left the city already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By all accounts, this city is very large,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but there must be a reason why she hasn't shown up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone kidnapped her and is holding her captive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me. Is your sister really pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can you please think about something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw through you before you invited me to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we understand each other, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're not exactly ugly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought that perhaps your sister is good looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And if she's not pretty, then you won't help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,she's as ugly as sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no better woman than my sister in the whole of Toras!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you find her, I can't even reward you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, kid. Your sister will be responsible for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you doing this from kindness or from greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, trust me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've observed how you helped this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very adept with your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's nothing special. I'm just lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've got some skill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a very good fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask for your help with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry. I already have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll ask you another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Yurius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's Yamato Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamato Takeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who broke the curse of Strawberry Fields?{and after that, of Penny Lane?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be confusing me with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be him, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They say he's very large and quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Allegedly, everyone who meets him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,respects him just because of his appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And every woman who crosses his path
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,supposedly wants to give herself to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. You can't be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's actually pretty rude of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like someone I knew, eerily similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately, that man has already died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Such things happen sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people who say
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that every person has a double in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Takeru, will you help me after you've completed your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to look for a place to crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and what if you run into the guys from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Innkeeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it? {no flowerly language in the Japanese}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks very much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please find something else for the boy to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be easy to find \Nsomething better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have a couple of pieces of clothing from my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to sleep in the same room as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest whatsoever in that direction, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! What's this?! Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The room is located on the second floor, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come with me, Jodi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they're hiding in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wait until they're asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise it's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope this is gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they're asleep, they won't stand a chance against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately to the right is the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodi, you can bathe first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But I don't want to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get cleaned up,\N no one will recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, it's not exactly pleasant for me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to sleep next to a little stinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But it's all right. I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't argue, buddy.\NCome on, get undressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's all right! Let go of me! I can do that myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But the door is to remain remain closed. Is that {\i1}clear{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no desire to look at you, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No education is also an education.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting like a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you perhaps have a room available?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible I'd like a room next to those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that can be arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me. I've brought fresh clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These are rather modest items.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The main thing is that they're clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourselves comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl? I don't believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru. Takeru! Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Takeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God, Jodi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad. I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,J-J-Jodi, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Jodi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get dressed now, or you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, put something on quickly, Jodi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me, Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't just say something like that. It isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodi, that doesn't have anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want to help me find my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you... that my sister is a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want her to take you away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl tricked us pretty good, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If we'd caught her right away, then we'd be in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at that. She's quite pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like that woman so much, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So this bitch has the drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:18:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be a traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But he has the strength of a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru, please! You can't just stop like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute, Jodi. I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably regard me rather badly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not true, Jodi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what's your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice, huh? A beautiful name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice, I accept this down payment for my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start looking for your sister tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So make sure you rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard of soldiers receiving 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,their pay before completion of their mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They only get a down payment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I like you, Jodice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,After we've saved your sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my reward, Jodice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know very well that I love women, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't like it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,when they indulge me only out of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, my darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that the advance was too small?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you really want it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss me, Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Jodice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru! Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru! Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lovely sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what I wanted to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't keep perfectly still, I'll cut the little one's throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.35,0:23:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I made myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Takeru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.26,0:23:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your sword aside. Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.98,0:23:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:24:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Very reasonable. Nice and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, but don't hurt Jodice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.60,0:24:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're finally silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.52,0:24:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You, close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.66,0:24:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.93,0:24:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.12,0:24:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What was all that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.67,0:24:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, little one,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.24,0:24:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,give back what you stole yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.98,0:24:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do I have to cut your ears off?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.16,0:24:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't hurt me. I don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.23,0:25:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should we start with your cute little nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.12,0:25:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my... God!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.29,0:25:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven't found anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.73,0:25:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet. But what's left to search here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.86,0:25:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Is everything okay in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.34,0:25:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why now? We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.21,0:25:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the girl and her clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.22,0:25:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.26,0:25:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.65,0:25:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.07,0:25:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.10,0:26:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell can they have hidden it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.70,0:26:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a bit early to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.90,0:26:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you finally found something?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.87,0:26:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.76,0:26:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably have to take care of you in a special way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.89,0:26:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.80,0:26:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That hurts! Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.07,0:26:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.26,0:27:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.72,0:27:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.89,0:27:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you finally willing...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.69,0:27:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell me where you hid what you stole from the priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.30,0:27:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I returned everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.66,0:27:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you take anything out of the bag? Be honest, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.60,0:27:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.61,0:27:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear! I didn't take anything! Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.02,0:28:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, you're pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.83,0:28:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry. This won't leave any scars on your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.46,0:28:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.72,0:28:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.54,0:28:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're extremely sensitive, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.46,0:28:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now try not to faint again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.03,0:28:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That would spoil all of my fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.92,0:28:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give your sweet little behind a good thrashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.48,0:28:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.54,0:28:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.02,0:29:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me go. I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.12,0:29:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.28,0:29:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After I've rested a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.61,0:29:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll transform you into a really lewd woman, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.21,0:30:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl knows nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.55,0:30:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Shade continuing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.84,0:30:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shade clearly wants to turn the girl into a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.35,0:30:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When Shade's finished with her, she'll be given a spoonful of the drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.06,0:30:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl will get so turned on that she'll obey blindly,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.52,0:30:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,despite all the perversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.96,0:30:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think Shade's being\N particularly cruel in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.18,0:30:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's probably something about the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.92,0:30:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet that the priest won't be allowed to touch her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.38,0:30:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He battered the last girl pretty badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.87,0:30:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God our bosses have different preferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.32,0:30:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we can earn our bread, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.56,0:30:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.03,0:30:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My head is buzzing horribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.00,0:30:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.20,0:31:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's... Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.32,0:31:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't shout so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.03,0:31:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.81,0:31:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And where's the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.87,0:31:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.06,0:31:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did you\N get this stuff? Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.30,0:31:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better tell me where Jodice is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.07,0:31:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you obtain this forbidden drug? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.84,0:31:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't like your answer, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.85,0:31:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Forbidden drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.65,0:31:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,From the mandrake plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.11,0:31:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give a woman just a single spoonful,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.19,0:31:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll automatically become a slave to her desires,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.37,0:31:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and she'll do everything she's told, no matter how perverted it may be!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.68,0:31:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a ultra-mega-cool thing. Very handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.34,0:32:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.09,0:32:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the work of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.10,0:32:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What does {\i1}that{\i0} mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.52,0:32:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really that stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.89,0:32:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that demonic forces are in town to party.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.49,0:32:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurius, tell me where Jodice is! I must find her quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.97,0:32:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.27,0:32:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.74,0:32:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yurius!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.18,0:32:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I need to dress myself up like a lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.23,0:32:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't simply demand that Jodice be returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.57,0:32:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.80,0:32:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you the posh girl and I'm the younger sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.14,0:32:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look in the mirror for once, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.58,0:32:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! I feel discriminated against!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.56,0:32:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to behave so conspicuously!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.08,0:32:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but are you sure that Jodice is hidden in the cathedral?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.89,0:32:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.73,0:33:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The new priest here belongs to some obscure religious order.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.12,0:33:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a very strange guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.45,0:33:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best to go have a look around and behave as if we want to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.08,0:33:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the least conspicuous way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.46,0:33:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.23,0:33:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.00,0:33:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.34,0:33:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We've lost our parents to a terrible disease
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.90,0:33:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and wanted to ask the priest to pray for their salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.93,0:33:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, the evil afflicting our family may be lifted from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.70,0:33:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My goodness. Not bad, Yurius.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.93,0:33:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my sincere condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.32,0:33:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll take you to the priest at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.58,0:33:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.82,0:33:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.78,0:34:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! How beautiful! You are welcome in God's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.53,0:34:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will pray for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.76,0:34:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shade will accompany both of you to the prayer hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.06,0:34:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shade?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.55,0:34:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.62,0:34:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.34,0:34:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shade? So you as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.31,0:34:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.99,0:34:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's my turn next!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.81,0:34:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.49,0:34:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body and your mind already belong to the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.03,0:34:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you waiting for, Shade?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.61,0:34:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.78,0:34:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.89,0:34:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! You can't kill me! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.77,0:34:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.18,0:34:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Shade?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.24,0:35:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurius, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.97,0:35:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to get the priest to tell you where they're hiding Jodice!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.55,0:35:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.93,0:35:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to fight me, I won't spare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.70,0:35:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you beast! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.06,0:35:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.58,0:35:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! You must be the legendary Takeru Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.37,0:35:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.46,0:35:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you figured out!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.29,0:35:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.46,0:35:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Die now!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.15,0:36:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.01,0:36:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.93,0:36:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.63,0:36:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you'll get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.15,0:36:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurius!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.09,0:36:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest, where's Jodice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.36,0:37:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll soon be handed over to Master Leonardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.09,0:37:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her, Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.08,0:37:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor little thing has no strength left to speak anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.54,0:37:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But before you can see her, I'll have to give you to Master Leonardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.06,0:37:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her away!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.15,0:37:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurius!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.83,0:37:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's that? What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.09,0:37:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.97,0:37:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.37,0:37:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's to blame,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.10,0:38:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.34,0:38:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.41,0:38:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Jodice...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.56,0:38:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice, I'm sorry I'll never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.86,0:38:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was Jodice's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.50,0:38:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.89,0:38:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Leonardo will atone for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.06,0:38:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.17,0:39:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.16,0:39:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everything's all right, Jodice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.70,0:39:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru... at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.13,0:39:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice, what's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.29,0:39:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me, Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.09,0:39:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.61,0:39:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.99,0:39:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together. What have they done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.70,0:39:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to do it with her, or she'll go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.25,0:39:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.05,0:39:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the effect of the mandrake.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.59,0:39:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice, they poisoned you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.52,0:39:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.01,0:39:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.54,0:39:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Almighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.09,0:40:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of hell did that girl go through?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.93,0:40:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.54,0:40:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.41,0:40:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.21,0:40:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole body's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.64,0:40:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it. Soon you'll feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.61,0:40:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.70,0:40:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry. Did I hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.78,0:40:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.57,0:40:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please put your hand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.26,0:40:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come already?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.11,0:40:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.44,0:40:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it feels great. Touch me there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.25,0:40:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.33,0:40:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.77,0:41:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! Continue, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.88,0:41:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You taste so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.71,0:41:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru! Hurry! Put it in quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.38,0:41:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.47,0:41:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.05,0:41:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.88,0:41:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.25,0:41:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.59,0:41:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.12,0:41:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru, please, don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.06,0:41:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my G-God!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.63,0:41:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.86,0:41:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad, Takeru, that finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.08,0:41:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good, Jodice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.91,0:41:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! This is so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.54,0:41:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, more... faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.23,0:41:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It feels good! More. More!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.33,0:41:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.25,0:41:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to come! Oh, it's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.16,0:42:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru! Takeru! Oh God!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.39,0:42:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let's come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.25,0:42:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God, Takeru! Faster! Harder!{I'm making this up...}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.73,0:42:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.00,0:42:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru... I'm... I-I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.91,0:42:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Jodice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.56,0:42:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the effect finally abated?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.36,0:42:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. My work here is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.69,0:42:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.36,0:42:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then come with me! I need to go to Rona.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.99,0:42:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to take care of Jodice first though.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.08,0:42:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.87,0:42:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rona, huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.16,0:42:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of her.\NI'll get Silver and go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.22,0:43:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Her Highness, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.43,0:43:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And you're the daughter of the Guardian of Rikyuu, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.48,0:43:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm glad you remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.45,0:43:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister suffered terribly,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.69,0:43:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and unfortunately, we were too late to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.62,0:43:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But because that nefarious priest is dead, this city is safe again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.63,0:43:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to remain here for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.56,0:43:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.56,0:43:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.93,0:43:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, as you saw, there will be no peace
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.14,0:43:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as Leonardo is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.81,0:43:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Takeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.37,0:43:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.18,0:43:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fight Leonardo together.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.33,0:43:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.19,0:43:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.15,0:43:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The freedom-loving, swashbuckling, legendary warrior Takeru Yamato
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.05,0:43:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,continues on his journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.74,0:43:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He ventures further,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.71,0:43:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and he doesn't know where and when he will learn the truth about himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.27,0:43:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru Yamato is marked by the star of destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.79,0:44:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He continues to look for romance and adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.07,0:44:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the last of the true heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.00,0:44:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru Yamato travels further on his erratic way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.59,0:44:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will his journey lead him next?
